        "bio": "Joe in the Studio is the stage name of Yusif Aliyev, a multi-instrumentalist and songwriter crafting music that feels like it could've been pressed on vinyl in the late 60s but still speaks to today. Armed with guitars, piano, bass, and drums — plus a knack for raw storytelling — every note is written, recorded, and produced solo in his small home studio.",
